" leader+f to format rust file 
nnoremap <silent> <leader>f :w<CR>:call system('rustfmt ' . shellescape(expand('%')))<CR>:edit<CR>

" Set 2 space for Rust tab
autocmd FileType rust setlocal shiftwidth=2 tabstop=2 expandtab

